  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/6351c29ba5e7a5807c729e97120a903e.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=188 /></span><br>For the nights you spend looking for your wings.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/96e913d04c9779e983245455335fd90f.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br>This isn't like that. Fight off relentless squares. Start simple, end simple. What happens in between? Everything else.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/a598879bcab83c24ed3beb3f44c195fd.poster.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/a598879bcab83c24ed3beb3f44c195fd.webm?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/a598879bcab83c24ed3beb3f44c195fd.mp4?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/053c787cb14d3964a2964f3c1a5219e0.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br>Buy \"School Coffee\", \"Eye Surgery\", \"Regret\" or whatever upgrade you might need to beat your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/6821f9b36e3b24b4f64efcc687033550.poster.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/6821f9b36e3b24b4f64efcc687033550.webm?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/6821f9b36e3b24b4f64efcc687033550.mp4?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/2bd7a8f5ec9a5f3cbabb9f028ca23439.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br>Find unique wings and unleash your true power.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/64097c598ffd72bae837b22434822c1d.poster.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/64097c598ffd72bae837b22434822c1d.webm?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/64097c598ffd72bae837b22434822c1d.mp4?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/9ffd964598f41d09b32b3d9bf8157ec9.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br>Complete the museum of everything.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/d65214ad8eb567566a6a751183b129f6.poster.avif?t=1745953498\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/d65214ad8eb567566a6a751183b129f6.webm?t=1745953498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992110/extras/d65214ad8eb567566a6a751183b129f6.